name: Marion County Health Department
tweet: Marion County Health Department is offering the Pfizer-BioNTech COVID-19 booster at our NEW satellite clinic located at 1343 Locust Avenue, Fairmont, WV 26554. The vaccine is available by appointment only for those who meet the CDC Booster requirements.
